---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-[#FAF7F2] px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl border-t border-[#2D3436]/5 pt-16 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
      <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-[#84A59D]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-[#84A59D]"></div>
      </div>
      <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#2D3436]">
        Psicologia Viva
      </span>
    </div>
    
    <p class="max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#2D3436]/50 font-light mb-10">
      Acolhendo sua história com respeito e profundidade. Atendimentos presenciais e online.
    </p>

    <div class="flex gap-8 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2D3436]/30 mb-16">
      <a href="#sobre" class="hover:text-[#84A59D] transition-colors">A Especialista</a>
      <a href="#abordagem" class="hover:text-[#84A59D] transition-colors">Abordagem</a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-[#84A59D] transition-colors">Privacidade</a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#2D3436]/20">
      © {currentYear} Psicologia Viva • CRP 06/123456
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
